<lb n="1118a06" ed="T"/><cb:juan fun="open" n="001"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>佛說當來變經</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="T" n="1118a07"/>
<lb n="1118a08" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="1118002" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">（（西晉…譯））十一字＝（（竺法護譯））四字【宋】【宮】，（（西晉三藏法師竺法護譯））十字【元】【明】，〔西晉…譯〕－【聖】</note><app n="1118002" cb:word-count="11"><lem wit="【大】">西晉月氏國三藏竺法護譯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">竺法護譯</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">西晉三藏法師竺法護譯</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】"><space quantity="0"></space></rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="1118a09" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT12p1118a0901">聞如是：</p><p xml:id="pT12p1118a0904" rend="inline">一時，佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園，與
<lb n="1118a10" ed="T"/>大比丘眾俱，比丘五百及諸菩薩。</p>
<lb n="1118a11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT12p1118a1101">爾時，世尊告諸比丘：「將來之世，當有比丘因
<lb ed="T" n="1118a12"/>有一法不從法化，令法毀滅，不得長益。何謂
<lb ed="T" n="1118a13"/>為一？不護禁戒，不能守心，不修智慧，放逸其
<lb n="1118a14" ed="T"/>意，唯求<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="1118003" type="orig">善＝華【宮】</note><app n="1118003"><lem wit="【大】">善</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">華</rdg></app>名不順道教，不肯<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="1118004" type="orig">勤＝謹【宋】【元】</note><app n="1118004"><lem wit="【大】">勤</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">謹</rdg></app>慕度世之
<lb n="1118a15" ed="T"/>業。是為一事，令法毀滅。」</p>
<lb n="1118a16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT12p1118a1601">佛告比丘：「復有二事，令法毀滅。何謂為二？一、
<lb n="1118a17" ed="T"/>不護禁戒，不攝其心，不修智慧，畜妻養子，放
<lb ed="T" n="1118a18"/>心恣意，賈作治<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="1118005">生＝產【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="1118005" resp="CBETA">生＝產【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118005"><lem wit="【大】">生</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">產</rdg></app>以<note type="orig" n="1118006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">共相＝相供【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">共相＝相供【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118006"><lem wit="【大】">共相</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">相供</rdg></app>活。二、伴黨相著，
<lb ed="T" n="1118a19"/>憎奉法者，欲令<note n="1118007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">陷＝墜【宮】</note><app n="1118007"><lem wit="【大】">陷</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">墜</rdg></app>墮故為言<note type="orig" n="1118008" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">義＝儀【三】，議【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="1118008" type="mod">義＝儀【宋】【元】【明】，＝議【宮】</note><app n="1118008"><lem wit="【大】">義</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">儀</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">議</rdg></app>，謂之<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="1118009" type="orig">諛＝諭【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="1118009"><lem wit="【大】">諛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">諭</rdg></app>諂；
<lb ed="T" n="1118a20"/><note n="1118010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">內＋（私）【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="1118010" type="mod">內＋（私）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="1118010"><lem wit="【大】">內</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">內私</rdg></app>犯惡<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="1118011" type="orig">〔行〕－【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="1118011">〔行〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118011"><lem wit="【大】">行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"></space></rdg></app>，外<note n="1118012" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">佯＝揚【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note type="mod" n="1118012" resp="CBETA">佯＝揚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="1118012"><lem wit="【大】">佯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">揚</rdg></app>清白。是為二事，令法毀
<lb ed="T" n="1118a21"/>滅。」</p>
<lb n="1118a22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT12p1118a2201">佛告<note n="1118013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔諸〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note resp="CBETA" n="1118013" type="mod">〔諸〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="1118013"><lem wit="【大】">諸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"></space></rdg></app>比丘：「復有三事，令法毀滅。何謂為
<lb ed="T" n="1118a23"/>三？一、既不護<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="1118014" type="orig">〔禁〕－【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="1118014" type="mod">〔禁〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118014"><lem wit="【大】">禁</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"></space></rdg></app><note type="orig" n="1118015" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">戒＝病【宋】，〔戒〕－【聖】</note><app n="1118015"><lem wit="【大】">戒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">病</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"></space></rdg></app>，不能攝心，不修<note n="1118016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">智慧＝經義【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="1118016" type="mod">智慧＝經義【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118016"><lem wit="【大】">智慧</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">經義</rdg></app>。二、
<lb n="1118a24" ed="T"/><note n="1118017" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">自＝白【聖】</note><app n="1118017"><lem wit="【大】">自</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">白</rdg></app>讀文字不<note n="1118018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">識＝諦【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note type="mod" n="1118018" resp="CBETA">識＝諦【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="1118018"><lem wit="【大】">識</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">諦</rdg></app>句<note type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="1118019">逗＝讀【宋】</note><app n="1118019"><lem wit="【大】">逗</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">讀</rdg></app>，以上著下、以下著上，
<lb n="1118a25" ed="T"/>頭尾顛倒，不能解了義之所歸，自以為是。三、
<lb ed="T" n="1118a26"/>明者呵之不從其教，反懷瞋恨，謂相嫉妬；<note type="orig" n="1118020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">識義＝議識【聖】</note><app n="1118020"><lem wit="【大】">識
<lb ed="T" n="1118a27"/>義</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">議識</rdg></app>者少，多不別理，<note type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="1118021">咸＝成【元】</note><app n="1118021"><lem wit="【大】">咸</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">成</rdg></app><note type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="1118022">云＝自【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="1118022" resp="CBETA">云＝自【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118022"><lem wit="【大】">云</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">自</rdg></app>為是。是為三事，令
<lb n="1118a28" ed="T"/>法毀滅。」</p>
<lb ed="T" n="1118a29"/><p xml:id="pT12p1118a2901">佛告<app corresp="#1118013" type="star"><lem wit="【大】">諸</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"></space></rdg></app>比丘：「復有四事，令法毀滅。何謂為
<pb n="1118b" xml:id="T12.0395.1118b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1118b01" ed="T"/>四？一、將來比丘<note n="1118023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（（已捨…業））十二字＝（（捨空閑處修道之業））八字【聖】</note><app cb:word-count="12" n="1118023"><lem wit="【大】">已捨家<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="1118024" type="orig">〔業〕－【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="1118024">〔業〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118024"><lem wit="【大】">業</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"></space></rdg></app>，在空閑處不修
<lb n="1118b02" ed="T"/>道業</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">捨空閑處修道之業</rdg></app>。二、憙遊人間憒閙之中，行<note type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="1118025">來＋（比丘）【三】【聖】</note><note type="mod" n="1118025" resp="CBETA">來＋（比丘）【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="1118025"><lem wit="【大】">來</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】">來比丘</rdg></app>談言，求好
<lb ed="T" n="1118b03"/>袈裟五色之服。三、高<note type="orig" n="1118026" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">聽＝望【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="1118026" type="mod">聽＝望【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="1118026"><lem wit="【大】">聽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">望</rdg></app>遠視以為綺<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="1118027" type="orig">雅＝飾【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="1118027" resp="CBETA">雅＝飾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118027"><lem wit="【大】">雅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">飾</rdg></app>，自
<lb ed="T" n="1118b04"/>以高德無能及者，以雜<note n="1118028" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">碎＋（之）【元】【明】</note><app n="1118028"><lem wit="【大】">碎</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">碎之</rdg></app>智<note n="1118029" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">〔比〕－【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1118029"><lem wit="【大】">比</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"></space></rdg></app>日月<note type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="1118030">之明＝比丘【宋】，之比丘【元】，〔之明〕－【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="1118030">之明＝比丘【宋】，＝之比丘【元】，〔之明〕－【宮】</note><app n="1118030"><lem wit="【大】">之明</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">比丘</rdg><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">之比丘</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"></space></rdg></app>——
<lb ed="T" n="1118b05"/>畜已！四、不攝三事，不護根門，行婦女間，宣文
<lb ed="T" n="1118b06"/>飾辭多言合<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="1118031" type="orig">偶＝禍【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1118031"><lem wit="【大】">偶</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">禍</rdg></app>，以動人心，使清變濁；身行
<lb n="1118b07" ed="T"/>荒亂，正法廢遲。是為四事，令法毀滅。」</p>
<lb ed="T" n="1118b08"/><p xml:id="pT12p1118b0801">佛告比丘：「復有五事，令法毀滅。何謂為五？
<lb n="1118b09" ed="T"/><note type="orig" n="1118032" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">〔一〕－【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="1118032" resp="CBETA">〔一〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118032"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"></space></rdg></app>、或有比丘本以法故，出家修道，廢深經教
<lb n="1118b10" ed="T"/>——十二因緣、三十七品，方等深妙玄虛之慧，智
<lb ed="T" n="1118b11"/>度無極，善權方便，空、無相、願至化之<note n="1118033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">節＝第【聖】</note><app n="1118033"><lem wit="【大】">節</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">第</rdg></app>。二、
<lb n="1118b12" ed="T"/>反習雜句淺<note n="1118034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔末〕－【宮】</note><app n="1118034"><lem wit="【大】">末</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"></space></rdg></app>小<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="1118035" type="orig">經＋（輩）【宮】</note><app n="1118035"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">經輩</rdg></app>、世俗行故——<note type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="1118036">王＝三【三】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="1118036">王＝三【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="1118036"><lem wit="【大】">王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">三</rdg></app>者經典，
<lb n="1118b13" ed="T"/>亂道之原——好講此業，易解世事，趣得人心令
<lb n="1118b14" ed="T"/>其歡<note n="1118037" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">喜＝悅【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="1118037" resp="CBETA">喜＝悅【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118037"><lem wit="【大】">喜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">悅</rdg></app>，因致名聞。<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="1118038" type="orig">〔三〕－【宋】【宮】，三＝四【元】【明】</note><app n="1118038"><lem wit="【大】">三</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"></space></rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">四</rdg></app>、新聞法人、淺解之士，
<lb n="1118b15" ed="T"/>意用妙快；深達之<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="1118039" type="orig">士＝人【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="1118039" resp="CBETA">士＝人【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118039"><lem wit="【大】">士</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">人</rdg></app>，不用為<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="1118040" type="orig">佳＝法【聖】</note><app n="1118040"><lem wit="【大】">佳</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">法</rdg></app>。<note type="orig" n="1118041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">〔四〕－【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note type="mod" n="1118041" resp="CBETA">〔四〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="1118041"><lem wit="【大】">四</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】"><space quantity="0"></space></rdg></app>、天龍鬼
<lb ed="T" n="1118b16"/>神不以為喜，心懷悒慼，口<note n="1118042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">發斯＝能發【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="1118042" type="mod">發斯＝能發【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118042"><lem wit="【大】">發斯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">能發</rdg></app>言：『大法欲滅，
<lb n="1118b17" ed="T"/>故使其然。』捨妙<note n="1118043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">法化＝化法【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="1118043" type="mod">法化＝化法【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118043"><lem wit="【大】">法化</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">化法</rdg></app>，反宣雜句，諸天流淚，速
<lb ed="T" n="1118b18"/>逝而去。五、<note type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="1118044">由＋（說）【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">由＋（說）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118044"><lem wit="【大】">由</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">由說</rdg></app>是正法稍稍見捨，無精修者。是
<lb ed="T" n="1118b19"/>為五事，令法毀滅。」</p>
<lb ed="T" n="1118b20"/><p xml:id="pT12p1118b2001">佛告比丘：「吾滅度後，有此邪事十<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="1118045" type="orig">五＝四【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="1118045">五＝四【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118045"><lem wit="【大】">五</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">四</rdg></app>之亂，令
<lb ed="T" n="1118b21"/>法毀滅，一何痛哉！若有比丘欲諦學道，棄捐
<lb n="1118b22" ed="T"/>綺飾，不求名聞，質<note type="orig" n="1118046" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">朴＝科【三】</note><note type="mod" n="1118046" resp="CBETA">朴＝科【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="1118046"><lem wit="【大】">朴</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">科</rdg></app>守真，宣傳正經——佛之雅
<lb n="1118b23" ed="T"/>典深法之<note n="1118047" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">化＝辭【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="1118047" resp="CBETA">化＝辭【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118047"><lem wit="【大】">化</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">辭</rdg></app>不用多言，案<note type="orig" n="1118048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">本說＝其本【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="1118048" resp="CBETA">本說＝其本【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118048"><lem wit="【大】">本說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">其本</rdg></app>經不捨正
<lb ed="T" n="1118b24"/>句，希言屢中不失佛意——麁衣趣食，得美不甘，
<lb ed="T" n="1118b25"/>得麁不<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="1118049">惡＝<g ref="#CB01158"></g>【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1118049"><lem wit="【大】">惡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】"><g ref="#CB01158"></g></rdg></app>，衣食好醜，隨施者意，不以瞋喜；
<lb n="1118b26" ed="T"/><note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="1118050" type="orig">攝＝護【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="1118050" type="mod">攝＝護【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118050"><lem wit="【大】">攝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">護</rdg></app>身、口、意，守諸根門，不違佛教；<note type="orig" n="1118051" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">念＝壽【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="1118051" type="mod">念＝壽【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118051"><lem wit="【大】">念</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">壽</rdg></app>命甚<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="1118052" type="orig">矩＝短【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="1118052" type="mod">矩＝短【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】【CB】</note><app n="1118052"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】">短</lem><rdg wit="【大】">矩</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">短</rdg></app>，
<lb n="1118b27" ed="T"/>恍<note n="1118053" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">惚＝忽【聖】</note><app n="1118053"><lem wit="【大】">惚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">忽</rdg></app><note type="orig" n="1118054" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">以＝已【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="1118054" type="mod">以＝已【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118054"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">已</rdg></app>過，如夢所見，覺不知<note n="1118055" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">處＝虛【宋】</note><app n="1118055"><lem wit="【大】">處</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">虛</rdg></app>；三塗之難，
<lb n="1118b28" ed="T"/>不可稱計，勤修佛法猶救頭然；五戒、十善、六
<lb n="1118b29" ed="T"/>度無極、四等、四恩、智慧、善權，咸可<note n="1118056" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">精＝修【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118056" resp="CBETA" type="mod">精＝修【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118056"><lem wit="【大】">精</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">修</rdg></app>行。<note type="orig" n="1118057" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">雖＋（復後生）【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="1118057">雖＋（復後生）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118057"><lem wit="【大】">雖</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">雖復後生</rdg></app>
<pb xml:id="T12.0395.1118c" n="1118c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1118c01" ed="T"/>不值佛世，出家為道學不唐捐，<note type="orig" n="1118058" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">平＝卒【宮】</note><app n="1118058"><lem wit="【大】">平</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">卒</rdg></app>其本心，愍
<lb ed="T" n="1118c02"/><note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="1118059" type="orig">念＝哀【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="1118059" type="mod">念＝哀【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118059"><lem wit="【大】">念</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">哀</rdg></app>一切，十方蒙恩。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT12p1118c0208">佛說如是，諸比丘悲喜前
<lb n="1118c03" ed="T"/>自歸佛，作禮而去。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="1118c04" ed="T"/><cb:juan fun="close" n="001"><cb:jhead><title>佛說當來變經</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
